Use the standard library
This is how to fib of n:
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is 0
   End when
   Remember that a is 0
   Remember that b is 1
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this diff of n and 1 times:
      Remember that next is sum of a and b
      Remember that a is b
      Remember that b is next
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is b
Now you know
>>> fib of 10
55
>>> fib of 1
1
>>> fib of 8
21